{"tid":2149913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李桂華高級編劇提到一樣野：「多名傳媒高層用外國戶口財政上支援」。假設李編劇所講既唔係劇本，到底係邊間銀行向編劇告密呢？","createTime":"2020-08-10T16:16:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T02:39:03.000Z","uid":230104,"like":128,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"732b52a387c8eae89219c08d60087eed8ac7866a","tid":2149913,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"左邊係當年疑似偷取證物疑犯， 右邊係外國警察<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RuqYmsN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRuqYmsN.jpg&h=593cfa4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n編劇李桂華晚上表示，警方今日拘捕9男1女，年齡介乎23至72歲，國安處查到一個團伙，要求外國制裁香港，有兩男一女運作這個組織，多名傳媒高層用外國戶口財政上支援這團體。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得華為晚晚周投訴大貓銀行舉報事件？"},{"pid":"60fe49c63134dac79d2f0cb6b0acef6d9cc9d1ec","tid":2149913,"uid":230104,"like":51,"dislike":2,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T16:21:17.000Z","msg":"係咪有跨國銀行中國藉高層裡應外合表忠？"},{"pid":"76bd14beefd6fb7f6420b80e934484f9e24025e5","tid":2149913,"uid":94824,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:01:48.000Z","msg":"燒左隻獅仲唔夠？"},{"pid":"bd2281fbf6489a41bf30bf75616fa918f7c7e077","tid":2149913,"uid":41389,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"76bd14beefd6fb7f6420b80e934484f9e24025e5","tid":2149913,"uid":94824,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:01:48.000Z","msg":"燒左隻獅仲唔夠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:04:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />$10"},{"pid":"1f6d1da09354363d4e342f850a5d9274c76ab3ed","tid":2149913,"uid":333471,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T17:09:37.000Z","msg":"我人格保證，大貓銀行！"},{"pid":"f4ba11d3ad0a62a6e79682acd4df16a99a8bef89","tid":2149913,"uid":126317,"